Privacy Policy
Last Updated: [08/15/24]
BTMK s.r.o. ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our game applications, websites, or other services (collectively, the "Services"). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By accessing or using our Services, you agree to the terms of this policy.
1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Data:
We may collect personal data directly from you or from third parties with your consent. This includes, but is not limited to:
- Contact Information: Name, email address, country, or region.
- User-Generated Content: Files, videos, images, or other data you provide.
- Profile Information: Screen name, avatar, in-game achievements, and purchases.
- Survey Information: Feedback and ratings on our Services.
- Parental Information: Parent's email and PIN for parental controls.
1.2 Automatically Collected Data:
- Analytics Data: Interaction details with our games and Services.
- Device Data: Unique device ID, IP address, and technical diagnostic data.
- Location Data: Based on your IP address.
- Commercial Information: Purchase history and preferences.
1.3 Third-Party Data:
We may receive your data from third parties such as social media networks, advertising partners, and payment processors.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
- Provide and personalize our games and Services.
- Optimize the functionality and performance of our Services.
- Communicate with you about updates, offers, and promotions.
- Ensure legal compliance and protect our rights.
- Analyze and improve our Services.
3. How We Share Your Information
We may share your information with:
- Service Providers: For processing payments, providing analytics, and improving our Services.
- Business Partners: For marketing and promotional purposes.
- Legal and Safety Compliance: When required by law or to protect rights and safety.
- Ad Networks: To deliver personalized ads based on your usage.
4. Data Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.
5. Your Rights and Choices
Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict the processing of your data. You can also opt-out of receiving targeted ads or withdraw your consent where applicable.
6. Children's Privacy
Our Services are not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect data from them. Parents can control certain features using parental controls.
7. International Data Transfers
Your data may be stored and processed in locations outside your country. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data during such transfers.
8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes through our Services or other communication methods.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@rebel-games.io.
